text: Rani Mukerji (born 21 March 1978) is an Indian actress active in Bollywood. She has won 7 Filmfare awards. == Selected filmography == * Kuch Kuch Hota Hai (1998) * Saathiya (2002) * Yuva (2004) * Hum Tum (2004) * Veer-Zaara (2004) * Black (2005) * Bunty Aur Babli (2005) * Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna (2006) * No One Killed Jessica (2011) * Talaash: The Answer Lies Within (2012) * Mardaani (2014) * Hichki (2018) ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors
